  "text": "Genomic DNA was prepared from 15 mg of leaf tissue as described [CITATION_1] . RFLP on the tomato genomic DNA was done using the DNA markers TG479, TG585, TG517, CT22, and CT90 [CITATION_2] and cDNA clones pSlCrtR-b1, pSlCrtR-b2 (this work), and Psy1.",
